{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Book of Abominations</strong> is a monster collecting RPG that puts a dark, Eldritch horror themed spin on the genre. After arriving on the remote Halflight Isle to inherit a house left by a distant unknown relative, the player unwittingly unleashes the monster apocalypse from the pages of a dusty old tome. It is up to you to capture these abominations, explore this mysterious island and discover the secrets of the book.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/story_gif_narrow.gif?t=1730818860\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/about_section_header_-_COMBAT_trip_size.png?t=1730818860\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master your control over the Book of Abominations: battle and capture a series of grotesque yet adorably charming Eldritch horrors in fast-paced, dynamic JRPG inspired turn based combat!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fill your bestiary: capture Lovecraftian abominations and mutate them through combat encounters to take on more powerful forms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize each monster's array of attacks and abilities to implement various status effects, buffs and debuffs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat bosses in one-off fights to gain powerful summons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a variety of charms to give your monster party unique advantages in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/combat_gif_shorter.gif?t=1730818860\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/about_section_header_-_EXPLORATION_trip_size.png?t=1730818860\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore Haflight Isle - a once prosperous fishing community shrouded in a history of supernatural, otherworldly horror.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet and befriend a colourful cast of NPCs, both humans and monsters alike!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find benevolent monsters and use the powers they bestow to solve puzzles and reach new areas of the island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover secrets in far-flung corners of the map, finding a variety of collectibles to assist in combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/Overworld_Gif_shorter_still.gif?t=1730818860\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730818860","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730818860","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/b3869ef6714aadca26ab0bc6d8c4be7cd0d18ebc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730818860","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/b3869ef6714aadca26ab0bc6d8c4be7cd0d18ebc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730818860","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Book of Abominations</strong> is a monster collecting RPG that puts a dark, Eldritch horror themed spin on the genre. After arriving on the remote Halflight Isle to inheri